// A field-less category marker, not a real widget. Native leaf builtins (Window/Button/TextArea/
// Text/MenuBar/MenuBarItem/Menu/MenuItem/TabView) declare `inherits NativeControl` purely to
// group themselves under this tag; it carries no fields and is never itself constructed. See
// docs/elwindui_spec.md 付録H.2 and `elwindui-codegen`'s `is_native` computation.
#[embedded]
component NativeControl {
}
